221
00:12:53,429 --> 00:12:56,364
You know, there's a difference
between, uh--

222
00:12:56,432 --> 00:13:00,459
You know, Mommy-- Mommy says
what we do and, and, uh,

223
00:13:00,536 --> 00:13:03,699
I have control
